metadata.description: Perspective - A collection of generative art that imagines how extraterrestrial lifeforms looks at space with their many pair of eyes. Following the path of our genesis collection where Constellation is created with a view of space from someone on Planet Earth. Have you wondered if there are life apart from planet Earth? What if we look at space from the multiple Perspectives of extraterrestrial lifeforms? How would space appear to them?
metadata.name: Perspective #1
